{"tid":2491244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《大公》社評促以國安法取締《蘋果》「依法取締《蘋果》等煽暴煽獨、挑戰國安法的媒體，已是刻不容緩。」","createTime":"2021-04-16T07:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:22:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7cf1f355f4479494d9fac628d0d5563cf0553f","tid":2491244,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"繼警務處處長鄧炳強昨日不點名批評《蘋果》「挑起香港仇恨」後，《大公報》社評今日（16日）亦以「依法取締《蘋果》 堵塞國安漏洞」爲題，點名稱《蘋果》以報道爲名宣傳港獨、挑戰國安法，要求「依法取締」。<br />\n<br />\n《大公報》刊登「資深評論員」方靖之的社評，先是稱中央透過成立國安法、「完善選舉制度」等同將香港「從萬丈深淵中拉回」，隨即將矛頭指向《蘋果》，稱一些媒體「利用其所謂第四權的身份，從事勾結外國實力、煽暴造假、挑戰國安的勾當」，其中《蘋果》扮演「最為惡劣、最爲猖狂的角色」，以報道之名，行為港獨宣傳、挑戰國安法之實。<br />\n<br />\n文章舉例指《蘋果》昨（15日）發佈的一篇有關重光團隊於倫敦刊登大型廣告的報道，「儼然是一片港獨組織的宣傳稿」，稱該報道「已經不是報道，而是政治宣傳、港獨宣傳」，質疑《蘋果》煽動港獨，「這樣的報道是否已經逾越了國安法的界線？」又指《蘋果》在反修例運動期間「公然造謠造假」有關8.31太子站、新屋嶺等事件，稱大批青年「被《蘋果》煽動而前途盡毀」，揚言「這筆賬必須跟《蘋果》這些媒體算清」。<br />\n<br />\n文章續指《蘋果》在國安法出台後抹黑、攻擊國安法，社評亦「走火入魔」，指《蘋果》辦報的目的就是「成為外國反華勢力的輿論機器，在香港煽風點火，從而配合反中亂港分子亂中奪權」，「奇怪的是，這樣一份報章仍然可以存在到今日，這不是咄咄怪事嗎？」稱港人需積極履行維護國家安全的義務，「該清算的就堅決清算」。文末總結指《蘋果》不除，香港國安便仍存在漏洞，「依法取締《蘋果》等煽暴煽獨、挑戰國安法的媒體，已是刻不容緩。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/LZDROGREGFGOLIA464EWSUFVV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FLZDROGREGFGOLIA464EWSUFVV4%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=f253c81c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FLZDROGREGFGOLIA464EWSUFVV4%2F&h=aff01255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/LZDROGREGFGOLIA464EWSUFVV4/</a>"},{"pid":"da93d727fb30c14f85304f416f63c0707464672a","tid":2491244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac46e1f03bf27ccbb1c670fe16bbcf6019a0ae6d","tid":2491244,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"又依法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958b76d64311f3e15e992d4735b8830375a55a1f","tid":2491244,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"封報館"},{"pid":"e02625784dc4ca145cd35d77a6d3d4a5dbe46d6f","tid":2491244,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"襯宜家仲有得睇好睇啦<br />\n好快立場 眾新聞 蘋果呢d都無埋"},{"pid":"f00f391d7abf2dd8078517c86a84e745cdc03b05","tid":2491244,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"文章續指《蘋果》在國安法出台後抹黑、攻擊國安法，社評亦「走火入魔」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太公報邊一日唔會走火入魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eeab551a56e37c10c74846b74aa180d87271de","tid":2491244,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"大公文匯先係背後治港之人<br />\n次次一吹雞就中硬"}]}